---
// Caso Studio: Convivio × Eleven Madison Park — mockup ristorante
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Caso Studio — Convivio | Ristorante Milano</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --bg: #f8f5f0;
      --dark: #0a0a0a;
      --green: #1d3828;
      --green-light: #2a5039;
      --gold: #c9a84c;
      --cream: #f8f5f0;
      --cream-dark: #e8e0d4;
      --text: #1a1a1a;
      --muted: #6b6356;
      --serif: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
      --sans: 'Space Grotesk', system-ui, sans-serif;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: var(--sans); overflow-x: hidden; }

    /* MOCKUP BAR */
    .mockup-bar {
      background: var(--dark); color: rgba(248,245,240,0.55);
      text-align: center; font-size: 0.75rem; padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem;
      font-family: var(--sans); letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    }

    /* BACK */
    .back-btn {
      position: fixed; top: 1.2rem; left: 1.5rem; z-index: 999;
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
      background: rgba(10,10,10,0.85); backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      color: rgba(248,245,240,0.75); text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 0.04em; padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 2rem; transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .back-btn:hover { color: var(--cream); }

    /* HERO */
    .hero {
      background: var(--dark); padding: 5rem 3rem 4rem;
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 4rem; align-items: end; min-height: 420px;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background-image: url('/images/portfolio/ristorante-hero.jpg');
      background-size: cover; background-position: center;
      opacity: 0.2;
    }
    .hero-left { position: relative; z-index: 2; }
    .hero-tag {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.7rem;
      font-size: 0.68rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .hero-tag::before { content: ''; display: block; width: 2rem; height: 1px; background: var(--gold); }
    .hero h1 {
      font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
      font-weight: 300; color: var(--cream); line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .hero h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold); }
    .hero-meta { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
    .hero-meta-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.15rem; }
    .hero-meta-label { font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(248,245,240,0.4); }
    .hero-meta-val { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--cream); }

    /* MAIN CONTENT */
    .main { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 3rem; }

    /* BRIEF */
    .brief-section { padding: 5rem 0 4rem; }
    blockquote {
      font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2.5vw, 1.8rem);
      font-weight: 300; font-style: italic; line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--text); border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
      padding-left: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .quote-attr { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--muted); padding-left: 2rem; }
    .quote-attr strong { color: var(--text); }
    .brief-p { margin-top: 2rem; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.9; color: var(--muted); max-width: 680px; }

    /* STEP */
    hr.step-sep { border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--cream-dark); margin: 2rem 0; }
    .step-label {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem;
      font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .step-num {
      width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--gold); color: var(--dark);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500; flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    /* STEP 1 */
    .step1 { padding: 3rem 0; }
    .insp-card {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 0; border: 1px solid var(--cream-dark);
      overflow: hidden; background: white;
    }
    .insp-screenshot { position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
    .insp-screenshot img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block; min-height: 320px; }
    .screenshot-label {
      position: absolute; bottom: 0.6rem; left: 0.8rem;
      background: rgba(10,10,10,0.7); color: rgba(248,245,240,0.9);
      font-size: 0.68rem; letter-spacing: 0.08em; padding: 0.3rem 0.6rem;
    }
    .insp-info { padding: 2.5rem; }
    .site-tag { font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .site-name { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
    .site-url { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .site-desc { font-size: 0.88rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem; }
    .tag { font-size: 0.68rem; letter-spacing: 0.08em; padding: 0.3rem 0.7rem; background: var(--cream); color: var(--muted); }
    .insp-quote { margin-top: 1.5rem; padding: 1rem 1.2rem; background: var(--cream); border-left: 2px solid var(--gold); }
    .insp-quote p { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 0.95rem; font-style: italic; color: var(--text); }
    .insp-quote cite { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--muted); display: block; margin-top: 0.4rem; }

    /* STEP 2 */
    .step2 { padding: 3rem 0; }
    .analisi-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
    .analisi-card { background: white; padding: 1.8rem; border: 1px solid var(--cream-dark); }
    .analisi-card h4 { font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .palette-swatches { display: flex; gap: 0.4rem; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
    .swatch { width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%; }
    .analisi-card p { font-size: 0.83rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--muted); }
    .font-demo { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .layout-diagram { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.3rem; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
    .layout-row { height: 12px; background: var(--cream-dark); border-radius: 2px; }
    .layout-row.full { width: 100%; }
    .layout-row.half { width: 55%; }
    .layout-row.short { width: 35%; }
    .layout-row.img { height: 48px; background: var(--cream); border: 1px solid var(--cream-dark); }

    /* STEP 3 */
    .step3 { padding: 3rem; background: var(--green); margin: 0 -3rem; }
    .traduzione-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
    .trad-col { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); padding: 2rem; border-top: 3px solid var(--gold); }
    .trad-col.changes { border-top-color: rgba(248,245,240,0.4); }
    .trad-col h3 { font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
    .trad-col.changes h3 { color: rgba(248,245,240,0.5); }
    .trad-col h4 { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }
    .trad-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.7rem; }
    .trad-list li { display: flex; gap: 0.8rem; font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.6; color: rgba(248,245,240,0.75); }
    .trad-list li::before { content: '✓'; color: var(--gold); flex-shrink: 0; font-weight: 600; }
    .trad-col.changes .trad-list li::before { content: '↗'; color: rgba(248,245,240,0.5); }

    /* STEP 4 */
    .step4 { padding: 3rem 0; }
    .risultato-intro { max-width: 620px; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
    .risultato-intro h3 { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
    .risultato-intro p { font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--muted); }
    /* Browser chrome */
    .demo-frame { background: white; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 8px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.12); border: 1px solid var(--cream-dark); }
    .demo-bar { background: #f0eeea; padding: 0.7rem 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .demo-dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .demo-dot.red { background: #ff5f57; } .demo-dot.yellow { background: #febc2e; } .demo-dot.green { background: #28c840; }
    .demo-url { flex: 1; text-align: center; font-size: 0.72rem; color: #888; font-family: monospace; background: white; padding: 0.2rem 0.8rem; border-radius: 4px; max-width: 220px; margin: 0 auto; }

    /* Convivio mini-site — EMP-inspired dark minimal */
    .conv-site-wrap { background: #080808; }
    .conv-nav {
      background: #080808; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      padding: 1.3rem 2.5rem;
    }
    .conv-logo { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.42em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #e8e0d4; font-weight: 300; }
    .conv-nav-link { font-size: 0.58rem; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(232,224,212,0.42); text-decoration: none; }
    /* Hero — large full-bleed, centered text overlay */
    .conv-hero { position: relative; height: 440px; overflow: hidden; }
    .conv-hero-img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block; filter: brightness(0.6); }
    .conv-hero-overlay {
      position: absolute; inset: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center;
    }
    .conv-hero-eyebrow { font-size: 0.57rem; letter-spacing: 0.24em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(232,224,212,0.5); margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }
    .conv-hero-title { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 3.2rem; font-weight: 300; color: #e8e0d4; font-style: italic; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 1.8rem; }
    .conv-hero-reserve { font-size: 0.58rem; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(232,224,212,0.65); border: 1px solid rgba(232,224,212,0.2); padding: 0.55rem 1.8rem; text-decoration: none; }
    /* Signature dish — photo + minimal text */
    .conv-signature { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; background: #0d0d0d; min-height: 300px; }
    .conv-sig-img { overflow: hidden; }
    .conv-sig-img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block; min-height: 300px; }
    .conv-sig-text { padding: 3.5rem 2.8rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; border-left: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04); }
    .conv-sig-eyebrow { font-size: 0.57rem; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(232,224,212,0.28); margin-bottom: 1.4rem; }
    .conv-sig-name { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 300; color: #e8e0d4; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 0.7rem; }
    .conv-sig-desc { font-size: 0.77rem; line-height: 2; color: rgba(232,224,212,0.42); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .conv-sig-price { font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.14em; color: rgba(232,224,212,0.28); }
    /* Reserve panel */
    .conv-reserve { padding: 4rem 2.5rem; text-align: center; background: #080808; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04); }
    .conv-reserve-eyebrow { font-size: 0.57rem; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(232,224,212,0.28); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .conv-reserve h3 { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 300; color: #e8e0d4; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.3; }
    .conv-reserve-sub { font-size: 0.72rem; color: rgba(232,224,212,0.35); margin-bottom: 2rem; letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
    .conv-reserve-cta { display: inline-block; font-size: 0.58rem; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #e8e0d4; border: 1px solid rgba(232,224,212,0.22); padding: 0.65rem 2rem; text-decoration: none; }

    /* CTA */
    .cta-section {
      padding: 5rem 3rem; text-align: center;
      background: var(--dark); margin: 4rem -3rem 0;
    }
    .cta-section .label { font-size: 0.68rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); display: block; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .cta-section h2 { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem); font-weight: 300; color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .cta-section p { color: rgba(248,245,240,0.55); font-size: 0.9rem; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto 2.5rem; line-height: 1.8; }
    .btn-gold {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
      background: var(--gold); color: var(--dark); text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.82rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 0.9rem 2.2rem; transition: background 0.2s; font-weight: 500;
    }
    .btn-gold:hover { background: #d4b460; }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 4rem 1.5rem 3rem; gap: 2rem; min-height: auto; }
      .main { padding: 0 1.5rem; }
      .insp-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .insp-screenshot img { min-height: 200px; max-height: 260px; }
      .analisi-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .step3 { margin: 0 -1.5rem; padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem; }
      .traduzione-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .conv-nav-link { display: none; }
      .conv-hero { height: 280px; }
      .conv-hero-title { font-size: 2rem; }
      .conv-signature { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .conv-sig-img img { min-height: 240px; max-height: 280px; }
      .cta-section { margin: 4rem -1.5rem 0; padding: 3.5rem 1.5rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="mockup-bar">🍽 Mockup di caso studio — Convivio è un brand di fantasia creato per illustrare il processo di lavoro</div>
  <a href="/dev/portfolio" class="back-btn">← Portfolio</a>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-left">
      <div class="hero-tag">Caso Studio</div>
      <h1>Dal rigore<br />di <em>Madison Park</em><br />a Milano</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-meta">
      <div class="hero-meta-item"><span class="hero-meta-label">Cliente</span><span class="hero-meta-val">Convivio — Milano</span></div>
      <div class="hero-meta-item"><span class="hero-meta-label">Settore</span><span class="hero-meta-val">Ristorante gastronomico</span></div>
      <div class="hero-meta-item"><span class="hero-meta-label">Ispirazione</span><span class="hero-meta-val">elevenmadisonpark.com</span></div>
      <div class="hero-meta-item"><span class="hero-meta-label">Durata</span><span class="hero-meta-val">3 settimane</span></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="main">
    <section class="brief-section">
      <blockquote>"Eleven Madison Park ha quel rispetto per il silenzio che voglio anche io. Ogni elemento guadagna il suo spazio. Non c'è nulla di superfluo. Voglio che chi apre il sito di Convivio senta subito che siamo seri, senza dover leggere niente."</blockquote>
      <p class="quote-attr"><strong>Luca Motta</strong>, chef-patron di Convivio</p>
      <p class="brief-p">Luca ha aperto Convivio tre anni fa nel quartiere Isola. Cucina contemporanea italiana, sala da 24 coperti, tutto su prenotazione. Il sito che aveva sembrava un ristorante qualunque. Eleven Madison Park gli ha mostrato come un sito può comunicare la stessa qualità che c'è nel piatto.</p>
    </section>

    <hr class="step-sep" />

    <section class="step1">
      <div class="step-label"><span class="step-num">1</span>Il Riferimento</div>
      <div class="insp-card">
        <div class="insp-screenshot">
          <img src="/images/portfolio/emp-screenshot.jpg" alt="Screenshot di Eleven Madison Park" />
          <div class="screenshot-label">elevenmadisonpark.com — screenshot reale</div>
        </div>
        <div class="insp-info">
          <div class="site-tag">Sito di Ispirazione</div>
          <div class="site-name">Eleven Madison Park</div>
          <div class="site-url">elevenmadisonpark.com</div>
          <p class="site-desc">Ristorante 3 stelle Michelin di New York, pianta 100% vegetale. Il sito è costruito con una disciplina visiva assoluta: un'unica fotografia che occupa tutto lo schermo, il logo in alto, quattro voci di menu. Nient'altro. La qualità si percepisce dall'assenza di compromessi.</p>
          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag">Full-screen photography</span>
            <span class="tag">Navigation minimale</span>
            <span class="tag">Nessun elemento decorativo</span>
            <span class="tag">Serif sottile</span>
            <span class="tag">Prenotazione in evidenza</span>
          </div>
          <div class="insp-quote">
            <p>"Non voglio foto di piatti con filtri Instagram. Voglio che il sito sia come il ristorante: essenziale, preciso, ogni elemento al suo posto."</p>
            <cite>— Luca Motta</cite>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="step-sep" />

    <section class="step2">
      <div class="step-label"><span class="step-num">2</span>L'Analisi</div>
      <div class="analisi-grid">
        <div class="analisi-card">
          <h4>Palette estratta</h4>
          <div class="palette-swatches">
            <div class="swatch" style="background:#f8f5f0"></div>
            <div class="swatch" style="background:#1a1a1a"></div>
            <div class="swatch" style="background:#1d3828"></div>
            <div class="swatch" style="background:#c9a84c"></div>
            <div class="swatch" style="background:#6b5c3e"></div>
          </div>
          <p>Off-white caldo, nero quasi assoluto. EMP usa pochissimi colori perché la fotografia porta già tutto. Per Convivio: verde bosco come accento identitario, oro per i dettagli di qualità.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="analisi-card">
          <h4>Sistema tipografico</h4>
          <div class="font-demo">Convivio</div>
          <p>Serif leggero spaziato per i titoli principali — richiama i menu tipografici dei ristoranti di alta cucina. Sans-serif geometrico per navigazione e informazioni pratiche.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="analisi-card">
          <h4>Pattern di layout</h4>
          <div class="layout-diagram">
            <div class="layout-row img" style="height: 60px;"></div>
            <div class="layout-row short" style="margin-top: 4px;"></div>
            <div class="layout-row half"></div>
            <div class="layout-row full"></div>
          </div>
          <p>Immagine dominante, titolo sottile al centro, pochissimo testo. Il bottone di prenotazione è sempre visibile ma non invasivo. La struttura rispetta l'intelligenza del visitatore.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="step3">
      <div class="step-label" style="padding-top:0;"><span class="step-num" style="background:var(--gold);color:var(--dark)">3</span><span style="color:rgba(248,245,240,0.6)">La Traduzione</span></div>
      <div class="traduzione-grid">
        <div class="trad-col">
          <h3>Cosa rimane</h3>
          <h4>Il rigore visivo di EMP</h4>
          <ul class="trad-list">
            <li>Fotografia full-screen come unico elemento narrativo della homepage</li>
            <li>Navigazione con quattro voci al massimo — nulla di superfluo</li>
            <li>Serif elegante e ariosa per tutti i testi principali</li>
            <li>Bottone prenotazione sempre accessibile, mai aggressivo</li>
            <li>Nessun elemento di urgenza o promozione visibile</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="trad-col changes">
          <h3>Cosa cambia</h3>
          <h4>L'identità di Convivio</h4>
          <ul class="trad-list">
            <li>Verde bosco come colore identitario — non il bianco sterile di EMP</li>
            <li>Luca è presente nella pagina About con il suo percorso</li>
            <li>Sezione stagionale: il menù cambia con le stagioni, il sito lo racconta</li>
            <li>Tono più caldo e narrativo — italiano, non americano distaccato</li>
            <li>Gallery dei piatti accessibile ma non sulla homepage</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="step4">
      <div class="step-label"><span class="step-num">4</span>Il Risultato</div>
      <div class="risultato-intro">
        <h3>convivio.it — il sito finale</h3>
        <p>Il rigore visivo di EMP tradotto in italiano: il verde bosco dell'Isola, il piatto come protagonista, Luca in primo piano. Stessa disciplina, identità tutta milanese.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="demo-frame" style="background:#080808;">
        <div class="demo-bar">
          <div class="demo-dot red"></div>
          <div class="demo-dot yellow"></div>
          <div class="demo-dot green"></div>
          <div class="demo-url">convivio.it</div>
        </div>
        <div class="conv-site-wrap">
          <!-- Nav — dark, minimalissimo -->
          <nav class="conv-nav">
            <a href="#" class="conv-nav-link">Riserva</a>
            <div class="conv-logo">Convivio</div>
